      {"@type":"Question","name":"Did the Child Tax Credit change for 2026?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The maximum credit increased from $2,000 per child to $2,200 per child starting with tax year 2025 under the One Big Beautiful Bill Act. This $2,200 amount also applies for 2026. The phase-out thresholds ($200,000 single / $400,000 MFJ) and the refundable cap ($1,700) are unchanged from 2025."}},
