        <h1>Child Tax Credit 2026: Amount, Rules, and Who Qualifies</h1>
        <p class="qa-meta">Updated June 2026 &nbsp;|&nbsp; OBBBA amounts confirmed &nbsp;|&nbsp; For 2026 returns filed in 2027</p>
        <p>The 2026 Child Tax Credit is $2,200 per qualifying child under age 17, made permanent by the One Big Beautiful Bill Act. Up to $1,700 per child is refundable as the Additional Child Tax Credit. The phase-out begins at $200,000 for single filers and $400,000 for married filing jointly.</p>
